00:48:07.708 --> 00:48:11.125
[bahasa Indonesia] Irfan kalau ke…

785
00:48:11.208 --> 00:48:16.666
Etni itu bagaimana? Kalau di tempat kerja.

786
00:48:16.750 --> 00:48:19.708
[tertawa]

787
00:48:19.791 --> 00:48:24.416
[tertawa] Sama saja. Maksudnya,
