01:15:46.541 --> 01:15:49.000
[Bude Fitri] Kenapa ribut sekali?

1123
01:15:51.625 --> 01:15:53.541
- Kenapa ini? Kok ribut?
- [debuk barang dipukul]

1124
01:15:56.875 --> 01:15:58.500
Aduh! Aku kejepit!

1125
01:15:58.583 --> 01:16:01.208
[bahasa Jawa] Rin? Ada apa?

1126
01:16:02.250 --> 01:16:04.583
- [bahasa Indonesia] Ada tikus!
- Ha? Tikus?

1127
01:16:04.666 --> 01:16:07.958
- [Ambu] Ada tikus, Bude!
- Di mana, Rin?

1128
01:16:08.041 --> 01:16:11.541
- Tikusnya besar, Bude.
- Rin! Aku takut, Rin!

1129
01:16:11.625 --> 01:16:14.708
- Ini tikusnya, Bude. Mau lihat?
- [berteriak] Irfan! Tidak!

1130
01:16:14.791 --> 01:16:16.916
Buang yang jauh, Fan. Aku takut.

1131
01:16:17.000 --> 01:16:21.291
[Bude Fitri bergidik]

1132
01:16:21.375 --> 01:16:22.416
Aduh!

1133
01:16:24.666 --> 01:16:25.750
[decit roda, gebrak]

1134
01:16:27.958 --> 01:16:28.916
[bernapas berat]

1135
01:16:29.000 --> 01:16:33.458
[musik menegangkan mengalun]

1136
01:16:42.333 --> 01:16:44.416
[kertak pintu ditutup]

1137
01:16:44.500 --> 01:16:46.791
Norma tidur, aku cuma
mau bicara dengan kamu…

1138
01:16:46.875 --> 01:16:50.208
Setelah ini, kamu mau lupakan semua itu,
terserah. Tolong, sebentar.

1139
01:16:50.291 --> 01:16:51.416
[menghela napas]

1140
01:16:51.500 --> 01:16:53.125
Aku tak bisa melupakan yang kemarin.

1141
01:16:53.208 --> 01:16:54.291
[bernapas berat]

1142
01:16:58.708 --> 01:16:59.833
Lalu apa?

1143
01:16:59.916 --> 01:17:01.208
[mengesah]

1144
01:17:02.958 --> 01:17:04.291
Kita bagaimana?

1145
01:17:04.375 --> 01:17:05.625
[mengesah]

1146
01:17:07.458 --> 01:17:09.250
Aku tak bisa begini terus.

1147
01:17:10.458 --> 01:17:12.000
[bernapas berat]

1148
01:17:29.708 --> 01:17:32.041
Tak ada yang minta kamu begini terus.

1149
01:17:36.208 --> 01:17:37.750
[Ambu] Keluar!

1150
01:17:46.000 --> 01:17:47.166
Lihat aku.

1151
01:17:47.250 --> 01:17:53.375
[musik dramatis mengalun]

1152
01:17:54.375 --> 01:17:55.250
[mengesah]

1153
01:17:58.333 --> 01:18:01.416
Katakan padaku kamu tak merasakan
apa yang aku rasakan.

1154
01:18:07.500 --> 01:18:09.250
Terus kita mesti apa?

1155
01:18:19.541 --> 01:18:21.458
[Irfan] Jujur pada perasaan kita.

1156
01:18:30.541 --> 01:18:32.916
[Irfan mengesah]

1157
01:18:35.708 --> 01:18:37.791
[kecupan berulang]

1158
01:18:38.375 --> 01:18:39.583
[Ambu terengah]

1159
01:18:41.000 --> 01:18:42.625
[debuk membentur dinding]

1160
01:18:43.458 --> 01:18:46.125
[debuk pelan]

1161
01:18:56.166 --> 01:18:57.208
Ambu?

1162
01:19:07.666 --> 01:19:08.750
[kecupan bergairah]

1163
01:19:08.833 --> 01:19:13.458
[musik dramatis berlanjut]

1164
01:19:13.541 --> 01:19:16.875
[kersak tirai bambu]

1165
01:19:21.000 --> 01:19:22.083
Ambu?

1166
01:19:26.958 --> 01:19:28.208
[ketukan pintu]

1167
01:19:32.625 --> 01:19:34.041
Norma masuk, ya?

1168
01:19:34.125 --> 01:19:40.000
[musik mengeras]

1169
01:19:43.291 --> 01:19:44.166
[kertak pintu ditutup]

1170
01:19:53.166 --> 01:19:54.208
[Norma] Ambu tak apa-apa?

1171
01:19:56.083 --> 01:19:57.333
Tak apa-apa.

1172
01:19:59.875 --> 01:20:01.208
Cuma lelah saja.

1173
01:20:02.291 --> 01:20:04.333
[mengesah]

1174
01:20:04.416 --> 01:20:08.375
Pasti lelah, Ambu. Warung lagi ramai.

1175
01:20:08.458 --> 01:20:10.166
Ambu belum sempat istirahat.

1176
01:20:10.666 --> 01:20:14.541
Mau Norma pijat? Selagi Aa Irfan lembur?

1177
01:20:14.625 --> 01:20:18.041
Tidak usah. Sudah, kamu tidur saja.

1178
01:20:18.125 --> 01:20:21.041
Besok hari pertama mengajar, 'kan?

1179
01:20:21.125 --> 01:20:22.041
[menghela napas]

1180
01:20:25.458 --> 01:20:27.583
Sudah sana, balik.

1181
01:20:29.250 --> 01:20:30.750
[menghela napas] Ya sudah.

1182
01:20:31.875 --> 01:20:33.875
Kalau ada apa-apa, bilang Norma.

1183
01:20:40.958 --> 01:20:42.125
[kertak pintu ditutup]

1184
01:20:42.208 --> 01:20:43.916
[menghela napas]

1185
01:20:44.000 --> 01:20:44.916
[kertak pintu ditutup]

1186
01:20:51.416 --> 01:20:52.250
[kertak jendela dibuka]

1187
01:20:55.833 --> 01:20:57.583
[terengah]

1188
01:21:00.500 --> 01:21:02.583
[bernapas berat]

1189
01:21:05.333 --> 01:21:07.875
[Irfan] Assalamualaikum, Neng. Aa pulang.

1190
01:21:07.958 --> 01:21:11.875
- [Norma] Waalaikumsalam.
- [Irfan] Neng, kamu belum tidur?

1191
01:21:11.958 --> 01:21:14.166
Menunggu Aa?

1192
01:21:14.250 --> 01:21:15.833
Sini, peluk dulu.

1193
01:21:15.916 --> 01:21:18.041
- [Irfan mengemu gemas]
- [terisak]

1194
01:21:18.750 --> 01:21:20.958
[Norma] Aa lelah? Sudah makan, belum?

1195
01:21:21.041 --> 01:21:23.291
[Irfan] Kebetulan belum makan.

1196
01:21:23.375 --> 01:21:26.375
[Irfan] Kamu mau masak?
Aa temani kamu masak, ya?

1197
01:21:30.791 --> 01:21:31.958
Aa.

1198
01:21:33.000 --> 01:21:36.333
Makan dulu, yuk. Neng masak satai bandeng.

1199
01:21:36.875 --> 01:21:38.833
Untuk bekal saja, Neng. Kesiangan.

1200
01:21:48.083 --> 01:21:51.500
- Ambu mana, Neng?
- Sudah pergi, pagi-pagi.

1201
01:21:53.500 --> 01:21:55.625
Subuh sudah mandi.

1202
01:21:55.708 --> 01:21:58.666
Katanya mau ke pasar dulu sebelum ke kios.

1203
01:21:59.375 --> 01:22:00.666
Segini nasinya?

1204
01:22:03.791 --> 01:22:05.500
Spesial untuk Aa.

1205
01:22:06.958 --> 01:22:08.166
[menghela napas]

1206
01:22:09.166 --> 01:22:11.666
- Assalamualaikum.
- Waalaikumsalam.

1207
01:22:13.375 --> 01:22:18.625
[musik dramatis mengalun]

1208
01:22:47.250 --> 01:22:53.000
[musik mengeras]

1209
01:22:57.833 --> 01:23:00.541
[keduanya terengah]

1210
01:23:11.125 --> 01:23:12.083
[kertak pintu dibuka dan ditutup]

1211
01:23:14.708 --> 01:23:15.875
- [berembus]
- [gemeletap langkah kaki]

1212
01:23:18.791 --> 01:23:19.791
Aa?

1213
01:23:26.875 --> 01:23:27.958
[menghela napas]

1214
01:23:28.458 --> 01:23:32.833
Neng rasa sudah saatnya
kita punya momongan, Aa. [tertawa kecil]

1215
01:23:43.666 --> 01:23:45.375
Malam ini libur dulu, ya, Neng?

1216
01:23:46.958 --> 01:23:48.583
Besok Aa harus berangkat pagi.

1217
01:23:48.666 --> 01:23:52.625
[musik sendu mengalun]

1218
01:23:53.291 --> 01:23:54.916
[Norma berembus]

1219
01:23:55.000 --> 01:23:56.000
Neng…

1220
01:23:57.541 --> 01:23:58.583
Tak apa-apa, 'kan?

1221
01:23:59.833 --> 01:24:00.666
[mengemu]

1222
01:24:03.166 --> 01:24:06.208
- [menghela]
- [derit tempat tidur]

1223
01:24:09.541 --> 01:24:16.041
[musik sendu berlanjut]

1224
01:24:27.833 --> 01:24:29.916
[bahasa Jawa] Kenapa pulang siang?

1225
01:24:37.125 --> 01:24:38.166
[bahasa Indonesia] Apa?

1226
01:24:38.250 --> 01:24:39.666
[tertawa kecil]

1227
01:24:39.750 --> 01:24:41.625
Sudah, nanti dia pulang.

1228
01:24:43.166 --> 01:24:45.833
Baru pukul dua.
Masih ada dua jam lagi, 'kan?

1229
01:24:46.791 --> 01:24:48.041
[keduanya tertawa]

1230
01:24:48.125 --> 01:24:49.916
- Ini, Neng!
- [bahasa Jawa] Terima kasih, Bu.

1231
01:24:50.000 --> 01:24:52.375
[bahasa Indonesia]
Terima kasih, sama-sama.

1232
01:24:55.958 --> 01:24:58.791
- Assalamualaikum.
- Eh? Waalaikumsalam.

1233
01:24:58.875 --> 01:25:01.041
- Dari mana, Fan?
- Dari kantor, Bude.

1234
01:25:01.625 --> 01:25:03.500
Aku mau mi ayamnya satu, lapar sekali!

1235
01:25:03.583 --> 01:25:04.583
Iya.

1236
01:25:04.666 --> 01:25:07.375
Itu rambut kenapa basah?
Kehujanan di mana?

1237
01:25:07.458 --> 01:25:11.083
[tertawa] Biasa, Bude.
Habis wudu, anak saleh.

1238
01:25:13.500 --> 01:25:17.833
Memang anak saleh. Pasti banyak wudu, ya?

1239
01:25:22.291 --> 01:25:25.625
- [bernapas berat]
- [mengemu]

1240
01:25:27.083 --> 01:25:30.916
- [Ambu mendesah]
- [derit tempat tidur]

1241
01:25:33.291 --> 01:25:34.250
[berbisik dalam bahasa Jawa] Itu dia!

1242
01:25:35.125 --> 01:25:36.875
Di sana!

1243
01:25:36.958 --> 01:25:38.208
[berbisik] Di mana?

1244
01:25:39.916 --> 01:25:41.041
[bahasa Indonesia] Ayo!

1245
01:25:41.541 --> 01:25:44.791
[musik menegangkan mengalun]

1246
01:25:44.875 --> 01:25:47.291
- Ini!
- Tenang.

1247
01:25:47.375 --> 01:25:48.875
- Ini kamarnya?
- Iya!

1248
01:25:48.958 --> 01:25:50.125
Pelan-pelan.

1249
01:25:53.666 --> 01:25:55.458
- Tidak kelihatan!
- Ya?

1250
01:25:58.416 --> 01:26:00.166
- Tidak mau!
- [mendesut]

1251
01:26:00.750 --> 01:26:01.791
- Biar kelihatan!
- Apa kau ini?

1252
01:26:02.375 --> 01:26:06.000
- [Ambu terkekeh]
- [derit tempat tidur]

1253
01:26:06.083 --> 01:26:08.583
[berseru pelan]

1254
01:26:12.000 --> 01:26:13.208
Ayo, cepat!

1255
01:26:13.291 --> 01:26:14.833
- [bahasa Jawa] Sudah kelihatan?
- [bahasa Indonesia] Sut! Diam.

1256
01:26:15.833 --> 01:26:16.750
[Bude Fitri] Ayo!

1257
01:26:18.666 --> 01:26:23.208
[Ambu mendesah, melenguh]

1258
01:26:25.541 --> 01:26:28.458
- [berbisik] Ada suara perempuan.
- [berbisik] Bagaimana suaranya?

1259
01:26:28.541 --> 01:26:30.541
[mendesah]

1260
01:26:30.625 --> 01:26:32.375
- Yang benar?
- Iya.

1261
01:26:32.458 --> 01:26:35.666
Rekam!

1262
01:26:35.750 --> 01:26:36.708
[mendesut]

1263
01:26:37.666 --> 01:26:42.041
[keduanya tertawa]

1264
01:26:44.000 --> 01:26:45.083
Beri tahu aku, ya.

1265
01:26:45.166 --> 01:26:46.291
[mendesut]

1266
01:26:55.333 --> 01:26:58.666
[musik menegangkan mengeras]

1267
01:26:58.750 --> 01:26:59.916
Cepat!

1268
01:27:01.333 --> 01:27:03.000
[bahasa Jawa] Nah, jatuh!

1269
01:27:03.083 --> 01:27:03.958
[mendesut]

1270
01:27:04.791 --> 01:27:06.583
- Bagaimana, ya?
- [mendesut]

1271
01:27:07.375 --> 01:27:08.583
[bahasa Indonesia] Waduh!

1272
01:27:09.708 --> 01:27:11.500
Kalian sedang apa?

1273
01:27:11.583 --> 01:27:12.416
Rin.

1274
01:27:13.416 --> 01:27:16.916
Ini, mandikan… membersihkan…

1275
01:27:17.000 --> 01:27:20.416
Ponselnya kotor.
Layarnya, tadi disuruh Bude.

1276
01:27:20.500 --> 01:27:22.250
Disuruh Bude, apa?

1277
01:27:22.333 --> 01:27:27.583
Begini, Rin. Di dalam kamarnya Irfan,
ada suara perempuan. Benar.

1278
01:27:27.666 --> 01:27:30.458
- Bagaimana tadi? [mendesah]
- [mendesah]

1279
01:27:30.541 --> 01:27:32.208
Ayo kita gerebek!

1280
01:27:32.291 --> 01:27:33.875
- Bude!
- Ayo kita gerebek!

1281
01:27:33.958 --> 01:27:36.500
[bahasa Jawa]
Ini pasti dengan si Etni itu!

1282
01:27:36.583 --> 01:27:39.791
Firasatku selalu kuat, tak pernah meleset!

1283
01:27:40.500 --> 01:27:41.916
Di mana kamarnya Irfan?

1284
01:27:42.000 --> 01:27:43.583
- [bahasa Indonesia] Itu kamarnya?
- Iya.

1285
01:27:44.083 --> 01:27:46.291
Fan, keluar kamu!

1286
01:27:46.375 --> 01:27:49.000
- Fan?
- Keluar!

1287
01:27:49.083 --> 01:27:52.333
Kalau kau tak keluar,
aku dobrak pintu ini!

1288
01:27:52.416 --> 01:27:53.791
- Dobrak, ya!
- [mengerang]

1289
01:27:54.416 --> 01:27:55.500
Fan!

1290
01:27:55.583 --> 01:27:56.541
- [Yahya berseru]
- [gubrak pintu didobrak]

1291
01:28:04.333 --> 01:28:05.416
[Irfan terkesiap]

1292
01:28:08.041 --> 01:28:09.166
Ada apa?

1293
01:28:09.916 --> 01:28:12.333
- Ada siapa di sini?
- Ada siapa?

1294
01:28:12.958 --> 01:28:13.791
Ada aku.

1295
01:28:13.875 --> 01:28:18.166
Tadi si Yahya dengar ada
suara perempuan di sini. Ya, 'kan, Yahya?

1296
01:28:18.833 --> 01:28:20.916
- Perempuan, Bude?
- Cari!

1297
01:28:22.708 --> 01:28:23.916
[Bude Fitri] Buka semua lemari!

1298
01:28:27.125 --> 01:28:28.333
Bawah kolong.

1299
01:28:31.625 --> 01:28:33.000
Ada apa ini, Bude?

1300
01:28:33.541 --> 01:28:34.458
Bude.

1301
01:28:36.875 --> 01:28:39.625
Irfan, kenapa kamu setiap siang pulang?

1302
01:28:40.458 --> 01:28:43.916
Istirahatnya satu jam, Bude.
Memang salah istirahat di rumah?

1303
01:28:44.000 --> 01:28:46.458
[mencemoh] Pasti ada
yang kamu sembunyikan.

1304
01:28:46.541 --> 01:28:48.625
Yahya mendengar
di sini ada suara perempuan.

1305
01:28:48.708 --> 01:28:50.291
Samar-samar, sepertinya…

1306
01:28:50.375 --> 01:28:51.666
Kita cari di luar!

1307
01:28:51.750 --> 01:28:52.583
Ayo!

1308
01:28:53.458 --> 01:28:55.041
[Bude Fitri] Awas, ya. Pokoknya aku cari.

1309
01:28:55.125 --> 01:28:59.208
Kalau sampai ketemu,
tak akan kuampuni! Ayo cari!

1310
01:28:59.291 --> 01:29:01.083
- Ayo cari ke belakang.
- Ya.

1311
01:29:01.166 --> 01:29:02.541
[Yahya] Bude, aku cari ke kamar mandi.

1312
01:29:02.625 --> 01:29:04.625
[Bude Fitri] Ya. Cari!

1313
01:29:04.708 --> 01:29:06.958
[bahasa Jawa] Di mana, ya?

1314
01:29:07.041 --> 01:29:09.458
- [Yahya berbahasa Indonesia] Tak ada.
- [Bude Fitri] Ha?

1315
01:29:09.541 --> 01:29:11.416
[bahasa Jawa] Terus dia di mana?

1316
01:29:11.500 --> 01:29:16.000
[bahasa Indonesia] Sudah, mendingan
sekarang kita masuk, minta maaf. Ayo.

1317
01:29:16.083 --> 01:29:18.083
[Bude Fitri] Hei, malah diseret-seret!

1318
01:29:18.166 --> 01:29:19.916
Maaf mengganggu istirahat.

1319
01:29:20.000 --> 01:29:22.500
Bude minta maaf,
ternyata kami salah dengar.

1320
01:29:22.583 --> 01:29:24.875
- Bagaimana ini? Seperti anak kecil!
- [mengemu]

1321
01:29:24.958 --> 01:29:27.291
Maaf sudah ganggu istirahatnya.
Tidur saja.

1322
01:29:27.375 --> 01:29:30.791
- Ayo, Bude. Ayo.
- Seperti anak kecil!

1323
01:29:31.708 --> 01:29:33.833
[Irfan] Seprai dan selimutnya
sudah aku ganti.

1324
01:29:34.750 --> 01:29:38.833
Aku yakin Irfan itu bohong!
Firasatku ini kuat!

1325
01:29:38.916 --> 01:29:41.791
Bude, mana buktinya?
Kita tak ada bukti, Bude!

1326
01:29:41.875 --> 01:29:45.500
Kamu sendiri mendengar
suara perempuan di dalam!

1327
01:29:46.041 --> 01:29:49.208
Iya, kalau itu perempuan asli.
Kalau perempuan jadi-jadian, bagaimana?

1328
01:29:49.291 --> 01:29:51.916
- Jangan menakutiku!
- Sini, Bude.

1329
01:29:52.000 --> 01:29:55.333
Anggap saja firasat Bude benar.
Kita berdua bicara ke Norma.

1330
01:29:55.416 --> 01:29:59.208
Norma dan Irfan cerai karena firasat Bude.
Apa Bude mau menanggung dosanya?

1331
01:29:59.291 --> 01:30:03.041
[plak]

1332
01:30:03.125 --> 01:30:06.333
Sebaiknya Bude fokus
pada ponsel Yahya. Ini mati total.

1333
01:30:07.125 --> 01:30:08.416
Bude mau belikan, 'kan? Menggantinya?

1334
01:30:08.500 --> 01:30:09.666
Stop!

1335
01:30:10.708 --> 01:30:14.625
- Menurut firasat Yahya, bisa diperbaiki.
- Perbaiki sana!

1336
01:30:14.708 --> 01:30:15.750
[bahasa Jawa] Permisi.

1337
01:30:16.833 --> 01:30:17.708
[mendengus]

1338
01:30:18.500 --> 01:30:21.625
- [bahasa Indonesia] Rumah digeledah?
- Iya, Neng!

1339
01:30:21.708 --> 01:30:23.791
- "Mengaku kamu! Ada siapa di sini?"
- [terkekeh]

1340
01:30:23.875 --> 01:30:26.291
"Yahya, periksa lemari, periksa kolong!"

1341
01:30:26.375 --> 01:30:30.791
Terus Bude sampai bilang, "Kamu kenapa
setiap siang pulang ke rumah?"

1342
01:30:30.875 --> 01:30:34.458
Aku jawab saja,
"Istirahatnya satu jam, Bude.

1343
01:30:34.541 --> 01:30:37.000
Memang salah istirahat di rumah?"
Iya, 'kan?

