1845
02:08:17.791 --> 02:08:20.625
Mari, Bu. Silakan.

1846
02:08:22.833 --> 02:08:27.000
[kersak kursi bergeser]

1847
02:08:31.916 --> 02:08:33.708
[menghela napas]

1848
02:08:39.291 --> 02:08:40.291
[berembus]

1849
02:08:45.000 --> 02:08:48.041
Sebagian uang
sudah Norma sisihkan di sini, Ambu,

1850
